secubox-core (1.1.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Add kiosk module (kiosk.py) for kiosk mode management
  * Add kiosk_status(), kiosk_enable(), kiosk_disable() functions
  * Add board detection: detect_board_type(), get_board_profile()
  * Add get_board_capabilities(), get_board_model() functions
  * Add interface classification: get_interface_classification()
  * Add get_physical_interfaces(), check_interface_carrier()
  * Supported boards: MOCHAbin, ESPRESSObin v7/Ultra, x64-vm/baremetal, RPi
  * Board profiles: "full" (high-end) or "lite" (embedded)
  * Library version bumped to 1.1.0

